---
const bars = [
  { label: "Savings", rate: "4%", value: "~$14,908", heightPct: 29 },
  { label: "5-yr CD", rate: "4.5%", value: "~$15,530", heightPct: 32 },
  { label: "Private credit", rate: "8%", value: "~$22,196", heightPct: 71 },
  {
    label: "Robert Ventures",
    rate: "10%",
    value: "~$27,070",
    heightPct: 100,
    featured: true,
  },
];
---

<section class="pres-cost">
  <div class="pres-cost__container">
    <div class="pres-cost__intro">
      <h2 class="pres-cost__heading">
        Safe money isn't safe if it's <em>quietly losing to inflation.</em>
      </h2>
      <p class="pres-cost__subhead">Same $10,000. Same ten years. Four endings.</p>
    </div>

    <ul class="pres-cost__chart" aria-label="Comparison of 10-year outcomes for $10,000">
      {
        bars.map((b) => (
          <li class={`pres-cost__row${b.featured ? " pres-cost__row--featured" : ""}`}>
            <div
              class="pres-cost__row-fill"
              style={`width: ${b.heightPct}%;`}
              aria-hidden="true"
            />
            <div class="pres-cost__row-content">
              <div class="pres-cost__row-meta">
                <span class="pres-cost__row-label">{b.label}</span>
                <span class="pres-cost__row-rate">{b.rate} &middot; 10 yrs</span>
              </div>
              <span class="pres-cost__row-value">{b.value}</span>
            </div>
          </li>
        ))
      }
    </ul>

    <div class="pres-cost__close">
      <p class="pres-cost__close-lead">
        In any single year, the difference looks small. Over ten, it's the difference between
        treading water and nearly tripling your money. The longer you wait in cash, the more of
        that gap you give up.
      </p>
      <p class="pres-cost__close-bridge">
        Compounding starts the day you invest, not the day you decide.
      </p>
    </div>

    <p class="pres-cost__disclaimer">
      Illustrative only. Figures compound monthly over 10 years on the principal shown, against a
      4% savings benchmark. Not a projection of future results.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .pres-cost {
    background: var(--bg-primary);
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .pres-cost__container {
    max-width: 1024px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 32px;
  }

  .pres-cost__intro {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .pres-cost__heading {
    font-family: "Roboto Serif", serif;
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text-heading);
    line-height: 120%;
    text-align: center;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .pres-cost__heading em {
    color: var(--green-dark);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .pres-cost__subhead {
    font-family: "Roboto", sans-serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-body);
    text-align: center;
    line-height: 150%;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .pres-cost__heading + .pres-cost__subhead {
    margin-top: -0.5rem;
  }

  .pres-cost__chart {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 14px;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 6px;
    background: var(--bg-primary);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
    border-radius: 12px;
  }

  .pres-cost__row {
    position: relative;
    display: block;
    padding: 14px 16px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
    isolation: isolate;
  }

  .pres-cost__row-fill {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0 auto 0 0;
    background: var(--green-tint);
    border-radius: 8px;
    z-index: -1;
  }

  .pres-cost__row--featured .pres-cost__row-fill {
    background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--green-brand), var(--green-hover));
  }

  .pres-cost__row-content {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .pres-cost__row-meta {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2px;
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .pres-cost__row-label {
    font-family: "Roboto", sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text-heading);
    line-height: 130%;
  }

  .pres-cost__row--featured .pres-cost__row-label {
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  .pres-cost__row-rate {
    font-family: "Roboto", sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .pres-cost__row--featured .pres-cost__row-rate {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
  }

  .pres-cost__row-value {
    font-family: "Roboto Serif", serif;
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-heading);
    line-height: 110%;
    font-variant-numeric: lining-nums tabular-nums;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .pres-cost__row--featured .pres-cost__row-value {
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  .pres-cost__close {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    max-width: 540px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .pres-cost__close-lead {
    font-family: "Roboto Serif", serif;
    font-size: 18px;
    color: var(--text-heading);
    line-height: 155%;
    text-align: center;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .pres-cost__close-bridge {
    font-family: "Roboto", sans-serif;
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--text-body);
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 150%;
    text-align: center;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .pres-cost__disclaimer {
    font-family: "Roboto", sans-serif;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 160%;
  }

  @media only screen and (min-width: 600px) {
    .pres-cost__container {
      padding: 4rem 2rem;
      gap: 40px;
    }

    .pres-cost__intro {
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .pres-cost__heading {
      font-size: 2.75rem;
    }

    .pres-cost__chart {
      padding: 18px;
      gap: 8px;
    }

    .pres-cost__row {
      padding: 18px 22px;
    }

    .pres-cost__row-label {
      font-size: 15px;
    }

    .pres-cost__row-value {
      font-size: 24px;
    }

    .pres-cost__close-lead {
      font-size: 20px;
    }

    .pres-cost__close-bridge {
      font-size: 16px;
    }
  }

  @media only screen and (min-width: 1136px) {
    .pres-cost__container {
      padding: 5rem 2rem;
    }

    .pres-cost__heading {
      font-size: 3.25rem;
    }
  }

  @media only screen and (min-width: 1920px) {
    .pres-cost__heading {
      font-size: 3.75rem;
    }
  }
</style>
